Class NioManagerDispatchThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • org.shared.net.nio.NioManagerThread
        • org.shared.net.nio.NioManagerDispatchThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Runnable, EnumStatus<NioManagerThread.NioManagerThreadStatus>, SourceLocal<NioEvent<?>>

    public class NioManagerDispatchThread
extends NioManagerThread
    A specialized NioManagerThread that dispatches newly created connections to NioManagerIoThreads.
